<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lal Pienni Muola Liemsa</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal pienni muol a liemsa,
 A hung vak kit tai;
 Muh ka nuom singkhuol luna,
 Van Lal cha hung pieng chu;
 Na sunga van Lal cha hung pieng chu,
 Chun liengthei Mari'n a chawi;
 Lal Immanuel chu.

[V2]
 * Chung nungpena chung nungpenah,
 Pathien lopi zing henla D.S.
 Amen, Amen, Pathien lopi zing henla Amen.

[V3]
 2. Kristmas ni a hung tun tieng,
 Bethlehem ka ngai;
 Bethlehem tang ngaih chulnung,
 Pak bangin a lun ie;
 Thangvan mite pakna zaila gi,
 Ka lunggilah a cham ie;
 Ngilhni umta puona.

[V4]
 3. Aw nang Bethlehem khawpi,
 Na hawih diek na e;
 Na sak min hi van nuoi ah,
 Aw chul thei ta puona;
 Thangvan aksi vakin ei pui hen,
 Bethlehem dai kawm achun;

[V5]
 4. Nausen deihum ka lunggil,
 Ah hung pieng kit hen;
 Chun thehnem in hui ingka,
 Ka kumsawt Lal dingin;
 Kumsawt in chamna hung leng tan tin;
 A min thiengtho pahchaknan;
 Daihni nei ta puonna.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>26</hymn_number>
</song>